<Base title="Requirements Management" description="Requirements management with constant need to adapt to target group demands – Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">Strategy</p>
<h1>Requirements Management with Constant Need to Adapt to Target Group Demands</h1>
<p>With this strategic service we help you to fulfil requirements, identify and minimise risks, and implement changes quickly and efficiently for your business model. This is possible on a daily basis with a database for a time history for individual requirements.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Requirements Management as Strategic Development by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>With good requirements management, you continuously coordinate the requirements fulfilled by your business model with those expected by the target group. The rapid developments in e-commerce require strategic keeping up. Without technical support, online shops quickly lose touch with the competition in their industry. With Shopware 6 and the requirements management features, you miss neither trends nor get strategically stuck on them for too long.</p>
<h2>Requirements Management as a Strategy in E-Commerce</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Risk management:</strong> With this you evaluate defined requirements for possible exclusion criteria or adjustment needs. With Shopware 6's feature, we enable the identification, analysis, quantification, aggregation, assessment and communication of risks. In this step you can manage them before they lead to a market disadvantage.</li>
<li><strong>Change management:</strong> Risk identified and eliminated – in the next requirements step, you develop new strategies, structures and processes with better error avoidance and better prospects for your online shop in market competition.</li>
<li><strong>Implementation management:</strong> On the basis of further analysis and adjustment developments, you can now position yourself in the market of your industry with low risk and good prospects.</li>
</ul>
<p>At the same time, you can use this to plan and realise projects, develop systems with few errors and efficiently, and define, analyse, document and validate requirements.</p>
<h2>Relevant Industries for Developments in Requirements Management</h2>
<p>Hardly any industry is subject to such rapid and strong changes and trends as fashion and lifestyle. Rapid reaction through technological advantage decides in e-commerce whether your online shop will find the acceptance tomorrow that it has built up today. With tight requirements management, you react in advance rather than afterwards to necessary changes. The service industry is a changeable barometer for market sentiment. The faster you can adapt to new requirements here, the better your corporate image is perceived as up to date.</p>
<h2>Benefits of Contemporary Requirements Management by Hob by Horse for Your Target Groups</h2>
<p>B2B wholesalers must immediately respond to new requirements from their retailers through their own adjustments. Consumer behaviour of end users is strongly controlled by marketing strategies of various industries. Through increasingly comprehensive offerings in e-commerce, the demands on product quality, delivery times and customer service are correspondingly high. With B2C requirements management you can adapt to this as well without any particular effort in time and money.</p>
<p><em>Do you need strategically advantageous requirements management? Find out more details from Hob by Horse by telephone or written <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">enquiry</a>!</em></p>
</div></div>
</Base>
